# Modified by Glefdar on 01-28: Plots highest GEX SPX strike on /ES instead of SPY. Added toggle to show strike bubbles. Also added automatic detection of premarket and label explaining that prev. day's OI is used during premarket, which replaced manual premarket toggle.

